<docbook><section><title>YouAreNotAllowedToConnectToADatabaseInDLC</title><para> </para><title> Error Message: You are not allowed to connect to a database in $DLC. (1379) </title> Error Message: <computeroutput>You are not allowed to connect to a database in $DLC. (1379)</computeroutput> 
<para>Clients cannot connect to Progress 9 databases which are hosted anywhere within the <computeroutput>$DLC</computeroutput> directory structure.</para><para>You should <computeroutput>cp</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>mv</computeroutput> your databases — and related files — to a &quot;<computeroutput>wrk</computeroutput>&quot; or other directory structure that resides parallel to — or above — <computeroutput>$DLC</computeroutput>.</para><para>This limitation does not exist in Progress 8 or earlier.</para><bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">Evidence</bridgehead>
